Feature: Filter products
  In order to filter products in the catalog
  As a user
  I need to be able to filter products in the catalog

  Background:
    Given the following family:
      | code      |
      | furniture |
      | library   |
    And the following products:
      | sku    | family    | enabled |
      | postit | furniture | yes     |
      | book   | library   | no      |
