    And a "book" product
    And a "book2" product
    And a "ebook" product
    And the following product attributes:
      | label       | required | translatable | scopable |
      | SKU         | yes      | no           | no       |
      | name        | no       | yes          | no       |
      | image       | no       | no           | yes      |
      | description | no       | yes          | yes      |
